"2016-10-14 15:14","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=33862479&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">TRACESPY 发表于 2016-10-14 15:11</font></a><br />\r\n我和你的看法有根本性的不同。我个人认为沟通不当只是次要矛盾，她们的根本矛盾是情感上的不对等。在别的 ...</div><br />\n沟通不当的核心问题是性格差太多，共同点太少，这样的关系在转折点肯定要出问题的，你和我说的差的不是太多，方向不一样。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1955","username":"alerbe","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"1884","dbdateline":"1476429268","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"33862529","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"人形灾害","authorid":"255706","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:15","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;amp;goto=findpost&amp;amp;pid=33862459&amp;amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">D．Va 发表于 2016-10-14 15:08</font></a></div><br />\n原来是肉村啊，差点以为是秀一鸡戴了个眼镜","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1956","username":"人形灾害","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"1885","dbdateline":"1476429342","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"33862533","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"alerbe","authorid":"98754","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:15","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=33862459&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">D．Va 发表于 2016-10-14 15:08</font></a></div><br />\n最后优子这个头巾有点像赫本的某个角色。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1957","username":"alerbe","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"1886","dbdateline":"1476429352","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"33862542","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"osore","authorid":"184969","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:17","message":"东山真的care和铠塚绝交吗，我看就像小黄和初中同学断联一样吧<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1958","username":"osore","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1887","dbdateline":"1476429437","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"33862543","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"奥柏伦亲王","authorid":"220348","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:17","message":"啊，真是日了狗，写了千来字的自己对希美和小天使的性格解读，一个手滑刷新全没了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face/31.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n这么说吧，希美当初的决定以观众角度来看是错误的，但当事人是个15岁小孩，而且正是被高三生的事情搞得有点走投无路的感觉，这时候的决定一定是非理性的，也是自我伤害式的，那么一年后，她认识到自己的错误，并且怀有复杂的情绪（认错，赎罪，报恩，以及捡现成的）来求明日香同意入部，也是出于她的个人感情，说是自我满足并无问题，但追求自我满足并没有错对吧。<br />\r\n霙和希美的关系是不对等的，也不是谁的错，人际关系总有扭曲的地方，而且远比动画描写的还要扭曲，相信两个人都有自知之明。希美有对不起霙的地方，但这和她想要回来并无冲突；霙因为这一年的郁结已经到了听到鞑靼人舞曲就无比痛苦的地步，但这个事情始终是她们两人之间的事情，希美她们没有把这两件事联系在一起，也是正常的。其实任何的误解往往都是几句话就能解决的事情，然而世上为什么还会有这么多亲朋好友因为一点误解而反目，因为不信任而成仇？人性是复杂的，人的面子是可笑的，人际关系就是这么的脆弱啊。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1959","username":"奥柏伦亲王","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"1888","dbdateline":"1476429443","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"33862572","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"michaellx1057","authorid":"263903","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:20","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=33858512&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">primavera 发表于 2016-10-14 08:56</font></a><br />\r\n话说，一开始小绿邀请小黄去游泳之前，小黄盯着起身走动的明日香看是有啥含义？ ...</div><br />\n我觉得因为泷老师让大家找家人要合宿许可，而明日香的不一定被母亲通过。之后涉及剧透就不说了。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1960","username":"michaellx1057","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"1889","dbdateline":"1476429621","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"33862586","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"eaglet_loki","authorid":"134856","dateline":"2016-10-14 15:21","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=33862459&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">D．Va 发表于 2016-10-14 15:08</fon